title: Chaulk O Lattey wins turf feature at Santa Anita
text:
Even-money favorite Chaulk O Lattey leads all the way to win turf feature at Santa Anita THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   8:52   8:52   
Subjects: 
California (1459) 

ARCADIA, California â€” Chaulk O Lattey led all the way to win the $55,000 feature by a neck at Santa Anita on Friday. 
Ridden by Rafael Bejarano, Chaulk O Lattey ran a mile on the turf in 1:37.09 and paid $4.20, $2.60 and $2.20 as the even-money favorite. 
Rattataptap returned $2.80 and $2.40, while Causeway Carolyn returned $2.80 to show. 
The victory, worth $42,900, increased Chaulk O Lattey's career earnings to $217,848, with four wins in nine starts for trainer Richard Baltas.
